<body lang=ZH-CN style='text-justify-trim:punctuation'>

<div class=Section1 style='layout-grid:15.6pt'>

<p class=MsoPlainText align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;color:white'>比十三张</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>一、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>游戏人数</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2-4</span><span
style='color:white'>人</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>二、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>扑克牌数</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>K</span><span
style='color:white'>、<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>、<span lang=EN-US>J</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>、<span lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span lang=EN-US>5</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span lang=EN-US>3</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2 </span>、<span
lang=EN-US>A</span>，每个牌各<span lang=EN-US>4</span>张；共计<span lang=EN-US>52</span>张。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>三、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>出牌规则</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>?&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>发牌</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>52</span><span
style='color:white'>张牌，每家<span lang=EN-US>13</span>张。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>?&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>摆牌</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>每一家<span lang=EN-US>13</span>张牌，规定时间内，摆好头道三张牌，接著中道、底道各为五张牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>而后依次开牌比较，头和头比，中和中比，尾和尾比。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>头道、中道、底道要求由小到大，否则称为‘倒道’犯规，各道都判为最小。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>如手牌为特殊牌型，可以选择免摆或手动摆牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>如选择免摆，则可以跳过头道、中道、底道的摆牌比较和比牌输赢，等其他玩家比牌结束后，最后才显示特殊牌型和结算；</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>如选择手动摆牌，则只结算头道、中道、底道的输赢道数，以及打枪和全垒打。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>?&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>胜负</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>头道赢者，加<span lang=EN-US>1</span>道；中道赢者，加<span lang=EN-US>1</span>道；底道赢者，加<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>如果普通牌型中比牌，出现同花顺等其他牌型，则直接以其他牌型的道数为准。例如同花顺、第二道中胜利，算<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>道，不计算<span lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>打枪</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>与其中一位玩家头道、中道、底道相比较，三道皆赢。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>假设此时对手总共扣<span lang=EN-US>3</span>道（普通牌），则：自己加<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>道。打一枪自己共赢<span lang=EN-US>6</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>假设此时对手总共扣<span lang=EN-US>18</span>道（三条<span
lang=EN-US>+</span>同花<span lang=EN-US>+</span>同花），则：自己加<span lang=EN-US>18</span>道。打一枪自己共赢<span
lang=EN-US>36</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全垒打</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3</span><span
style='color:white'>个人以上有该算分规则。三道与其他所有玩家相比三道全赢。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>输赢</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>最终输赢<span lang=EN-US>=</span>最后输赢道数<span
lang=EN-US>*</span>房间底分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>四、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>普通牌型</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>同花顺＞炸弹＞葫芦＞同花＞顺子＞三条＞两对＞对子＞散牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>同花顺</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>同门花色中之五张连续牌；若别家也有同花顺时，先比较顺子大小，如相同再比较花色大小；黑桃<span
lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>红心<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>梅花<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>方块。<span
lang=EN-US>5</span>道，在中道为<span lang=EN-US>10</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>炸弹</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>五张中里有四张同等级的牌；若别家也有，则比炸弹大小。<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>道，在中道为<span lang=EN-US>8</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>葫芦</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>即三带二，五张中有三张相同数字的牌及另外两张相同数字的牌；若别家也有，则比三张大小。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道，在中道为<span lang=EN-US>2</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>三条冲头道</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>头道为三张相同数字的牌。<span lang=EN-US>3</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>5.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>同花</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>五张牌是同一花色中任意五张牌；若遇相同则先比这副牌中最大的一支，如又相同再比第二支、依此类推。如牌型全部相同则以花色大小轮输赢。黑桃<span
lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>红心<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>梅花<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>方块。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>6.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>顺子</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='color:white'>五张牌数字连续的组合；<span lang=EN-US>A</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>、<span lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span lang=EN-US>5</span>为最小牌。<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>、<span lang=EN-US>J</span>、<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>K</span>、<span lang=EN-US>A</span>为最大牌，若巧遇别家也有则以最大那张牌的花色大小轮输赢。黑桃<span
lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>红心<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>梅花<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>方块。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>7.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>三条</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>由三张同一数字的牌和另外两张不同的牌组成。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>8.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>两对</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>牌型中五张牌由两组两张相同数字的牌所组成。若遇相同则先比这副牌中最大的一对，如又相同再比第二对、如又相同再比单张牌大小。如牌型全部相同以较大的对子的花色大小轮输赢，黑桃<span
lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>红心<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>梅花<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>方块。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>9.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>对子</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>牌型由两张相同数字的牌组成。若别家也相同则比剩下牌的数字大小，如牌型全部相同以对子的花色大小轮输赢，黑桃<span
lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>红心<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>梅花<span lang=EN-US>&gt;</span>方块。<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>10. </span><span
style='color:white'>散牌</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>无法组出任何牌型的五张单牌；<span lang=EN-US>A</span>最大，<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>最小。<span lang=EN-US>1</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>五、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>特殊牌型</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>发牌后，如手牌为特殊牌型，可选择跳过摆牌，免摆；</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>免摆后，不能同时参与打枪和全垒打，且判定为特殊牌型。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>1.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>青龙</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>13</span><span
style='color:white'>张手牌为全同花的一条龙；<span lang=EN-US>52</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>2.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全红</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为红桃或方块；<span lang=EN-US>26</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>3.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全黑</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为黑桃或草花；<span lang=EN-US>26</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>4.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全红一点黑</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌有<span lang=EN-US>12</span>张是黑的<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>张是红的；<span lang=EN-US>13</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>5.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全黑一点红</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌有<span lang=EN-US>12</span>张是红的<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>张是黑的；<span lang=EN-US>13</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>6.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>一条龙</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌为<span lang=EN-US>2</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>、<span lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span lang=EN-US>5</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span lang=EN-US>10</span>、、<span lang=EN-US>J</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>Q</span>、<span lang=EN-US>K</span>、<span lang=EN-US>A</span>；<span
lang=EN-US>13</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>7.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>五对一刻</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌为<span lang=EN-US>5</span>个对子，和<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个三张；<span lang=EN-US>9</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>8.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全小</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为<span lang=EN-US>2</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>、<span lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span lang=EN-US>5</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span lang=EN-US>10</span>，可以缺；<span lang=EN-US>6</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>9.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>全大</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为<span lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>、<span lang=EN-US>J</span>、<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>K</span>，可以缺；<span lang=EN-US>6</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>10. </span><span
style='color:white'>六对半</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌为<span lang=EN-US>6</span>个对子，和<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个单牌；<span lang=EN-US>6</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>11. </span><span
style='color:white'>半小</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为<span lang=EN-US>A</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>、<span lang=EN-US>3</span>、<span lang=EN-US>4</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>5</span>、<span lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span lang=EN-US>10</span>，可以缺；<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>12. </span><span
style='color:white'>半大</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>手牌全为<span lang=EN-US>6</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>7</span>、<span lang=EN-US>8</span>、<span lang=EN-US>9</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>、<span lang=EN-US>J</span>、<span lang=EN-US>Q</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>K</span>、<span lang=EN-US>A</span>，可以缺；<span lang=EN-US>3</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>13. </span><span
style='color:white'>三顺</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>中道及尾道为顺子，头道也是三张连续的顺子。<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>14. </span><span
style='color:white'>三花</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>中道及尾道为同花，头道也是三张相同的同花；<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>道。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span style='color:white'>六、<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>牌型大小</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>A.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>所有特殊牌型都比普通牌型大。直接赢普通牌型。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>B.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>相同道数之间的特殊牌型，打平。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>C.&nbsp; </span><span
style='color:white'>不同道数之间的特殊牌型，高道数的直接赢低道数的全部。</span></p>

<p class=MsoPlainText><span lang=EN-US style='color:white'>&nbsp;</span></p>

